Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.41,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:20.22,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.22,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.50,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:04.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.20,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:22.48,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:27.28,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:34.22,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she wearing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A purple dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to a lot of effort...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Wearing something different every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been one week. So, I'd like to start out by telling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...about my "rotation" for this week:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday... a long tailored jacket with a pleated skirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuesday... on open-collared blouse with a cardigan, both beige.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wednesday... a traditional single jacket-suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thursday... the uniform. And Friday, a cobalt green dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But this no more than a plan, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Depending upon my mood, I may change the "rotation".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother... The cherry blossoms are gone now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many fresh green leaves on the trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,2. The Glass Slippers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Another letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The letter! Aren't you still sending letters to your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's not my boyfriend, he's my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Same difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, a brother is a brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my brother is noisy and obnoxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dear brother is different...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But, my brother, she's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You are neither my boyfriend nor my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But on that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...the first snowfall of the season...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were someone I could not live without....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok everyone, you have 5 minutes to complete this quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You had been teaching us at cram school
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,for the past four weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your last day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely it wasn't love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When the last day came,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I realized that I might never see you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I just felt that I couldn't let you slip away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want you to be like all the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...entering my life and then leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't let that happen. I just couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Those eyes, those brown eyes, they somehow reflected my childhood days...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was those mysteriously shining brown eyes that attracted me to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...surely it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A question? Sure, On which page?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Be my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't bother you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just read... please just read my letters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And it would be great if you could write to me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you have the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't even have to write to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just read my letters, that would be more than enough! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I got the courage to do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... your name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Misonoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the daughter of Professor Misonoo of Jyoto University?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's keeping you, Henmi, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's snowing harder and harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry just a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... no... I mean, well, I've read a couple of his books...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's my address...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, but I'll expect the first letter to tell me that you got into High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,O... Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother... brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the warm feeling of that word...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been so longing for that feeling since childhood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that it became mine at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.68,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Seiran School, next stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tomoko! Listen! Next Sunday...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother is going to let us use the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's great! What's our challenge this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A chocolate cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good! With rum, nuts, and dried fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And fluffy whipped cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And decorated with mint leaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfect! That sounds wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go dutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been calling you. Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you always come to school at this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure I'm here to meet you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The first class is Mrs. Imai's. She's always early.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmph! "excuse" you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How pretty! Today's dress looks really nice on you, Misonoo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, big sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi! Good morning, pussy-cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"Pussy-cat"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The bell is ringing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Take your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...so anyway—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! You two, take your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You look so pretty when you are angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky you! Being scolded by Kaoru-no-Kimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, scold me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You, could you please move...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No big deal. I just want to sit next to Misonoo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet! Hurry! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take your things...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:35.63,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,One of the most interesting ways to get to London is through the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:38.43,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Of course, this country has its problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:41.60,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,So you may have problems too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:47.22,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,However, I prefer to think of them not as problems, but as adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy I get to sit next to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...regarding Mariko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,ever since orientation, I've been thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was something different about Mariko's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...that it's her lips. Her very red lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why are you looking at me that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Your lips... your lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I constantly bite my lips like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...because the big sisters like red lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So that... anyway, never mind... Perhaps you'd like to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What a gorgeous, but pushy girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And, somehow, also, mysterious...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu Mariko-san is so full of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, how much is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a big deal in my family
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,since my mother was also a Seiran Sorority member.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, a mother and daughter both in the Seiran Sorority!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I haven't been chosen yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a sure thing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I already begged my father until he let me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,get the dress made for the final selection party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, the Sorority of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's the day, during 5th period,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that they'll announce the candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Misaki was talking about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki Aya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, she's probably one of the top candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hate her, I really hate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had to put up with her being in my classes since Junior High!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's such a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,About me! Do you think I'll be selected?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I don't know much about the Sorority...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm quite sure of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorority membership...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the chosen few get to be in the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san and Misaki-san have been so pre-occupied...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I came to Seiran, I didn't even know sororities existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a new world for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that I know more about them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...I wonder if they are really such a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She saw me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...but she didn't even recognize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have forgotten already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Fifth period is starting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama! Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay. I see that you're as popular ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I'm no "Kaoru-no-Kimi"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your taste in clothing is no better than before, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have bourgeois tastes like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"Classy" is the term I prefer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What great pot-shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What great pot-shots! They're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in the basketball club?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so great about and dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my business... not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Later then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sorority has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, it's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, quiet please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I would now like to announce the names of the candidates for Seiran Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, would those ladies whose names I call be so kind as to come forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu Mariko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Congratulations! I knew you could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still just a candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And next...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And next... Orihara Kaoru-san
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, but I decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that? State your reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm opposed to the very existence of the Sorority itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But since it's not "politically correct"...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...to say that I'm opposed to the existence of this Sorority
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,let me just say instead that it's because of my poor health.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But thank you for stating your opinion so honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the final candidate from this class...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't agree with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.13,0:18:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Why isn't it fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Misonoo Nanako qualified for the Sorority?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So you think {\i1}you{\i0} are qualified?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut-up! You, the daughter of a pornography writer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since we were in Junior High,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known that Shinobu Hisaki
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is your father, and he's a porn writer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone knew that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We pretended as if we didn't know because we pitied you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you! Damn you! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if your family's school endowment is huge,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you're still not qualified for the Sorority,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and neither is Misonoo Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be nice if it were otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but children cannot choose their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh sister, I'm cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fret, it's ok. It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Our selection...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still oppose the fairness of our selection?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:19:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I can let you be a candidate as a replacement for Orihara Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,However, my one veto vote will guarantee that you won't be selected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Every year, it turns into a fight like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,From competition comes strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to survive this competition
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is itself a qualification for being selected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The final selection party is being held at noon this Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,At the Sorority House.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:21:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. This the invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Miso... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late! I've waited for over 20 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quite a scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole class went crazy over those announcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know! But along with Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:21:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.47,0:22:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.37,0:22:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I have to attend the party...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.44,0:22:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's next... Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.75,0:22:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.42,0:22:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But the cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We were supposed to bake the cake next Sunday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.31,0:22:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.85,0:22:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm sure I won't be selected.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.86,0:22:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Tomoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.80,0:22:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.87,0:22:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My little Nanako has become such a Cinderella-Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.61,0:22:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's show them they made a good choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home. The main gate will be closed soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't let everything end like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.92,0:23:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.86,0:23:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cinderella-Princess dropped her glass slippers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.86,0:23:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and became her everyday self when the clock struck twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.67,0:23:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When will the clock strike twelve for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.76,0:24:14.01,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.01,0:24:19.50,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.90,0:24:25.11,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.11,0:24:30.58,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.25,0:24:36.92,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.92,0:24:42.32,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.32,0:24:45.13,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.13,0:24:47.93,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.93,0:24:50.33,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.33,0:24:55.47,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.94,0:25:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The other girls react adversely to Nanako's selection to the Sorority...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.15,0:25:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...and a slanderous note is posted in response.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.02,0:25:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The day before the selection party, Nanako receives a phone call
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.24,0:25:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,from someone claiming to be Miya-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.17,0:25:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: Nanako is Disqualified?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.33,0:25:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
